public static interface Adjusting.XML.SAXResult extends Adjusting.XML.Result<SAXResult>
Adjusting version of a SAXResult.

The adjusting methods inherited from Adjusting.XML.Result will apply to any XML parser the implementation constructs to verify the content written, otherwise having no effect.
